  <entry>
    <title>互联网实验</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2023/01/02/%E4%BA%92%E8%81%94%E7%BD%91%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2023/01/02/%E4%BA%92%E8%81%94%E7%BD%91%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C/</id>
    <published>2023-01-02T06:50:32.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-01-02T11:52:20.215Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="39组"><a href="#39组" class="headerlink" title="39组"></a>39组</h1><h2 id="一、实验要求"><a href="#一、实验要求" class="headerlink" title="一、实验要求"></a>一、实验要求</h2><ol><li>拓扑中需要使用动态路由协议。</li><li>拓扑中需要包含VLAN以及Trunk技术。</li><li>拓扑至少包含设备：2台交换机、4台路由器、4台主机。</li><li>拓扑中设计较为复杂的网络技术(如ACL、NAT)等将有加分。</li></ol><h2 id="二、使用技术"><a href="#二、使用技术" class="headerlink" title="二、使用技术"></a>二、使用技术</h2><ul><li>VLAN路由连接</li><li>RIP路由协议</li><li>Trunk技术</li><li>NAT技术</li><li>ACL防火墙设置</li></ul><h2 id="三、实验目标"><a href="#三、实验目标" class="headerlink" title="三、实验目标"></a>三、实验目标</h2><ul><li>掌握路由器上启动RIP进程</li><li>掌握查看和调试RIP路由相关协议</li><li>深入了解交换机VLAN 配置</li><li>熟悉不同VLAN之间的路由配置</li><li>熟悉VLAN Trunk的配置</li><li>掌握静态NAT特征与配置</li><li>掌握ACL配置</li></ul><h2 id="四、实验内容"><a href="#四、实验内容" class="headerlink" title="四、实验内容"></a>四、实验内容</h2><p>配置RIP、VLAN、Trunk、ACL、NAT</p><h2 id="五、实验拓扑"><a href="#五、实验拓扑" class="headerlink" title="五、实验拓扑"></a>五、实验拓扑</h2><h2 id="六、实验步骤"><a href="#六、实验步骤" class="headerlink" title="六、实验步骤"></a>六、实验步骤</h2><h3 id="Step1：配置PC"><a href="#Step1：配置PC" class="headerlink" title="Step1：配置PC"></a>Step1：配置PC</h3><p>在“以太网”中找到ipv4协议，按照拓扑图修改各台PC的IP地址、子网掩码和默认网关：<br><strong>PC0：</strong></p><ul><li>IP地址：192.168.10.2</li><li>子网掩码：255.255.255.0</li><li>默认网关：192.168.10.1</li></ul><p><strong>PC1：</strong></p><ul><li>IP地址：192.168.20.2</li><li>子网掩码：255.255.255.0</li><li>默认网关：192.168.20.1</li></ul><p><strong>PC2：</strong></p><ul><li>IP地址：192.168.10.3</li><li>子网掩码：255.255.255.0</li><li>默认网关：192.168.10.1</li></ul><p><strong>PC3：</strong></p><ul><li>IP地址：192.168.20.3</li><li>子网掩码：255.255.255.0</li><li>默认网关：192.168.20.1</li></ul><h3 id="Step2：配置路由器"><a href="#Step2：配置路由器" class="headerlink" title="Step2：配置路由器"></a>Step2：配置路由器</h3><p><strong>配置Router1</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Router&gt;enable</span><br><span class="line">Router#config terminal</span><br><span class="line">Router(config)#hostname Router1</span><br><span class="line">Router1(config)#int f1/0</span><br><span class="line">Router1(config-if)#ip address 192.168.10.1 255.255.255.0</span><br><span class="line">Router1(config-if)#no shutdown</span><br><span class="line">Router1(config)#int s0/1</span><br><span class="line">Router1(config-if)#ip address 215.215.215.215.1 255.255.255.0</span><br><span class="line">Router1(config-if)#no shutdown</span><br><span class="line">Router1(config)#int s0/0</span><br><span class="line">Router1(config-if)#ip address 222.222.222.1 255.255.255.0</span><br><span class="line">Router1(config-if)#no shutdown</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//配置RIP</span><br><span class="line">Router1(config)#router rip</span><br><span class="line">Router1(config-router)#network 192.168.10.0</span><br><span class="line">Router1(config-router)#network 215.215.215.0</span><br><span class="line">Router1(config-router)#network 222.222.222.0</span><br><span class="line">Router1(config-router)#end</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>配置Router2</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Router&gt;enable</span><br><span class="line">Router#config terminal</span><br><span class="line">Router(config)#hostname Router2</span><br><span class="line">Router2(config)#int s0/1</span><br><span class="line">Router2(config-if)#ip address 222.222.222.2 255.255.255.0</span><br><span class="line">Router2(config-if)#no shutdown</span><br><span class="line">Router2(config)#int s0/0</span><br><span class="line">Router2(config-if)#ip address 223.223.223.1 255.255.255.0</span><br><span class="line">Router2(config-if)#no shutdown</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//配置RIP</span><br><span class="line">Router2(config)#router rip</span><br><span class="line">Router2(config-router)#network 222.222.222.0</span><br><span class="line">Router2(config-router)#network 223.223.223.1</span><br><span class="line">Router2(config-router)#end</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>配置Router3</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Router&gt;enable</span><br><span class="line">Router#config terminal</span><br><span class="line">Router(config)#hostname Router3</span><br><span class="line">Router3(config)#int s0/0</span><br><span class="line">Router3(config-if)#ip address 215.215.215.2 255.255.255.0</span><br><span class="line">Router3(config-if)#no shutdown</span><br><span class="line">Router3(config)#int s0/1</span><br><span class="line">Router3(config-if)#ip address 214.214.214.1 255.255.255.0</span><br><span class="line">Router3(config-if)#no shutdown</span><br><span class="line">Router3(config)#int s0/2</span><br><span class="line">Router3(config-if)#ip address 223.223.223.2 255.255.255.0</span><br><span class="line">Router3(config-if)#no shutdown</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//配置RIP</span><br><span class="line">Router3(config)#router rip</span><br><span class="line">Router3(config-router)#network 223.223.223.0</span><br><span class="line">Router3(config-router)#network 215.215.215.0</span><br><span class="line">Router3(config-router)#network 214.214.214.0</span><br><span class="line">Router3(config-router)#end</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>配置Router4</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Router&gt;enable</span><br><span class="line">Router#config terminal</span><br><span class="line">Router(config)#hostname Router4</span><br><span class="line">Router4(config)#int s0/1</span><br><span class="line">Router4(config-if)#ip address 214.214.214.2 255.255.255.0</span><br><span class="line">Router4(config-if)#no shutdown</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//配置RIP</span><br><span class="line">Router4(config)#router rip</span><br><span class="line">Router4(config-router)#network 214.214.214.0</span><br><span class="line">Router4(config-router)#end</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Step3：配置VLAN和Trunk"><a href="#Step3：配置VLAN和Trunk" class="headerlink" title="Step3：配置VLAN和Trunk"></a>Step3：配置VLAN和Trunk</h3><p><strong>配置Switch0</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Switch0#configure terminal</span><br><span class="line">Switch0(config)#int f0/2</span><br><span class="line">Switch0(config-if)#switchport mode access</span><br><span class="line">Switch0(config-if)#switchport access vlan 10</span><br><span class="line">Switch0(config)#int f0/3</span><br><span class="line">Switch0(config-if)#switchport mode access</span><br><span class="line">Switch0(config-if)#switchport access vlan 20</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>配置Switch1</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Switch1#configure terminal</span><br><span class="line">Switch1(config)#int f0/2</span><br><span class="line">Switch1(config-if)#switchport mode access</span><br><span class="line">Switch1(config-if)#switchport access vlan 10</span><br><span class="line">Switch1(config)#int f0/3</span><br><span class="line">Switch1(config-if)#switchport mode access</span><br><span class="line">Switch1(config-if)#switchport access vlan 20</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>Trunk配置</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Switch0(config)#int f0/1</span><br><span class="line">Switch0(config-if)#switchport mode trunk</span><br><span class="line">Switch0(config-if)#end</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Switch1(config)#int f0/1</span><br><span class="line">Switch1(config-if)#switchport mode trunk</span><br><span class="line">Switch1(config-if)#end</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Router(config)#interface g0/0/0</span><br><span class="line">Router(config-if)#no ip address</span><br><span class="line">Router(config-if)#no shutdown</span><br><span class="line">Router(config)#int g0/0/0.10</span><br><span class="line">Router(config-if)#encapsulation dot1q 10</span><br><span class="line">Router(config-if)#ip address 192.168.10.1 255.255.255.0</span><br><span class="line">Router(config)#int g0/0/0.20</span><br><span class="line">Router(config-if)#encapsulation dot1q 20</span><br><span class="line">Router(config-if)#ip address 192.168.20.1 255.255.255.0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>验证VLAN配置情况</strong></p><h3 id="Step4：配置静态NAT"><a href="#Step4：配置静态NAT" class="headerlink" title="Step4：配置静态NAT"></a>Step4：配置静态NAT</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Router1(config)#ip nat inside source static 192.168.10.2 222.222.222.4</span><br><span class="line">Router1(config)#ip nat inside source static 192.168.10.3 222.222.222.5</span><br><span class="line">Router1(config)#ip nat inside source static 192.168.20.2 222.222.222.6</span><br><span class="line">Router1(config)#ip nat inside source static 192.168.20.3 222.222.222.7</span><br><span class="line">Router1(config)#int f1/0</span><br><span class="line">Router1(config-if)#ip nat inside</span><br><span class="line">Router1(config)#int s0/0</span><br><span class="line">Router1(config-if)#ip nat outside</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>验证NAT配置情况</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Router1#show ip nat translations</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>用Router2 ping 222.222.222.4（PC0），ping通证明NAT配置正确</p><h3 id="Step5：配置ACL"><a href="#Step5：配置ACL" class="headerlink" title="Step5：配置ACL"></a>Step5：配置ACL</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Router3#config terminal</span><br><span class="line">Router3(config)#access-list 100 deny ip host 202.202.202.4 host 204.204.204.2</span><br><span class="line">Router3(config)#access-list 100 permit ip any any</span><br><span class="line">Router3(config)#int s0/1/1</span><br><span class="line">Router3(config-if)#ip access-group 100 in</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>验证ACL配置情况</strong></p><p>用主机0 （192.168.10.2）ping 204.204.204.2，无法ping通证明ACL配置正确</p><h2 id="七、功能总结"><a href="#七、功能总结" class="headerlink" title="七、功能总结"></a>七、功能总结</h2><p>通过RIP联通所有网段；</p><p>192.168.10.0网段和192.168.20.0网段通过VLAN技术相互通信；</p><p>其中192.168.10.0网段和192.168.20.0网段通过NAT技术将内网地址映射到222.222.222.0外网网段上地址与其他网段实现通信；</p><p>通过Router3设置ACL，实现阻断222.222.222.4到214.214.214.2的转发。</p><h2 id="技术补充"><a href="#技术补充" class="headerlink" title="技术补充"></a>技术补充</h2><h3 id="动态路由协议Rip"><a href="#动态路由协议Rip" class="headerlink" title="动态路由协议Rip"></a>动态路由协议Rip</h3><p>参考05：动态RIP</p><p>RIP Routing Information Protocol 路由信息协议</p><p>RIP是一种基于距离矢量（Distance-<a href="https://so.csdn.net/so/search?q=Vector&spm=1001.2101.3001.7020">Vector</a>）算法的协议，它使用跳数（Hop Count）作为度量来衡量到达目的网络的距离。RIP通过UDP报文进行路由信息的交换，使用的端口号为520。</p><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_38265137/article/details/80503512">https://blog.csdn.net/qq_38265137/article/details/80503512</a></p><p><img src="https://y6gbjg9hbn.feishu.cn/space/api/box/stream/download/asynccode/?code=M2JjZDljYzYwNjQyYjY4MjdhZDViMTRlYWU3MTcwMWFfcmRPYlU0UDJQSFNGUVMwQ29aeUlyU0lCUXJ4QVVJbTdfVG9rZW46Ym94Y252V0dwT2pGMEl5YmpxbVBYa1dwZWZoXzE2NzIyNDI1MjQ6MTY3MjI0NjEyNF9WNA" alt="img"></p><h3 id="VLAN"><a href="#VLAN" class="headerlink" title="VLAN"></a>VLAN</h3><p>参考07：VLAN间路由</p><p>VLAN（<a href="https://so.csdn.net/so/search?q=Virtual&spm=1001.2101.3001.7020">Virtual</a> Local Area Network）即虚拟局域网，是将一个物理的LAN在逻辑上划分成多个广播域的通信技术。VLAN内的主机间可以直接通信，而VLAN间不能直接通信，从而将广播报文限制在一个VLAN内。</p><h3 id="Trunk"><a href="#Trunk" class="headerlink" title="Trunk"></a>Trunk</h3><p>参考07：VLAN间路由</p><p>端口汇集</p><h3 id="ACL"><a href="#ACL" class="headerlink" title="ACL"></a>ACL</h3><p>参考09：ACL实验</p><p>访问控制列表ACL（Access Control List）是由一条或多条规则组成的集合。所谓规则，是指描述报文匹配条件的判断语句，这些条件可以是报文的源地址、目的地址、端口号等。 ACL本质上是一种报文过滤器，规则是过滤器的滤芯。设备基于这些规则进行报文匹配，可以过滤出特定的报文，并根据应用ACL的业务模块的处理策略来允许或阻止该报文通过。</p><h3 id="NAT"><a href="#NAT" class="headerlink" title="NAT"></a>NAT</h3><p>参考08：NAT网络地址转换</p><p>NAT ( Network Address Translation ) 中文意思是”网络地址转换”</p><h2 id="问题整理"><a href="#问题整理" class="headerlink" title="问题整理"></a>问题整理</h2><h3 id="VLAN-1"><a href="#VLAN-1" class="headerlink" title="VLAN"></a>VLAN</h3><p>不同的 Vlan 相互隔离广播域。</p><p>在二层交换坏境下，相同VLAN内的节点如果配置相同网段的IP地址即可直接通信。</p><p><strong>子接口实现跨VLAN访问</strong></p><p><img src="/images/%E8%B7%A8vlan%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE.png"></p><p>将GE0&#x2F;0&#x2F;1作为VLAN10用户的网关，GE0&#x2F;0&#x2F;2作为VLAN20用户的网关，可以实现两个VLAN的互访。</p><h3 id="TRUNK"><a href="#TRUNK" class="headerlink" title="TRUNK"></a>TRUNK</h3><p>将 Switch1 和 Switch2 之间的链路设置为Trunk链路。</p><p><strong>TRUNK的作用</strong></p><ol><li>传输VLAN</li><li>数据在trunk 链路上传输要打标签，数据在离开trunk 链路时要脱标签</li><li>通过 trunk 的标签可以区分不同的流量。</li><li>注意：trunk 工作在数据链路层（只能识别 mac 地址），不能实现不同 vlan 之间的通信</li></ol><p><strong>TRUNK端口与access端口的区别</strong></p><ul><li>access端口一般只属于一个vlan，用于连接pc或router</li><li>trunk可以允许多vlan通过，用于交换机之间</li></ul><h3 id="ACL-1"><a href="#ACL-1" class="headerlink" title="ACL"></a>ACL</h3><table><thead><tr><th align="left">指令</th><th align="left">用法</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left">配置access-list</td><td align="left">access-list [list number] [permit</td></tr><tr><td align="left">将指定访问列表应用到相关接口，并指定ACL作用的方向</td><td align="left">ip access-group {[access-list-number]&amp;#124;[name]} [int&amp;#124;out]</td></tr><tr><td align="left">显示已设置的访问控制列表内容</td><td align="left">show ip access-lists</td></tr></tbody></table><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Router3#config terminal</span><br><span class="line">Router3(config)#access-list 100 deny ip host 202.202.202.4 host 204.204.204.2</span><br><span class="line">Router3(config)#access-list 100 permit ip any any</span><br><span class="line">Router3(config)#int s0/1/1</span><br><span class="line">Router3(config-if)#ip access-group 100 in</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>ACL有什么用处</strong></p><ol><li>限制网络流量、提高网络性能；</li><li>提供网络安全访问；</li><li>可以在路由器端口决定哪种类型的通信流量被转发或被阻塞。</li></ol><p><strong>ACL配置原则</strong></p><p>一个ACL可以由多条“deny&#x2F;permit”语句组成，每一条语句描述一条规则，每条规则有一个Rule-ID。匹配顺序按照ACL的Rule-ID的顺序，<strong>从小到大</strong>进行匹配。</p><p>为每种协议、每个方向、每个接口配置一个ACL</p><p><strong>ACL命令解释</strong></p><ol><li>source address：主机ip地址</li><li>通配符掩码：“0”— 锁住。用来固定不能变的部分。“1”— 任意取值，用来表示放开的部分，不需要连续。</li><li>host：0.0.0.0</li><li>any：255.255.255.255</li></ol><p><strong>举例</strong></p><p><img src="/images/ACLexample.png"></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ip access0list extended test deny icmp 192.168.1.254 255.255.255.0</span><br><span class="line">int f0/0</span><br><span class="line">ip access-group test in</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
