  <entry>
    <title>数据结构复习</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2022/12/24/data-structure-review/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2022/12/24/data-structure-review/</id>
    <published>2022-12-24T09:34:58.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-12-24T09:52:30.816Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="chapter1"><a href="#chapter1" class="headerlink" title="chapter1"></a>chapter1</h2><h3 id="1-1-数据结构定义"><a href="#1-1-数据结构定义" class="headerlink" title="1.1 数据结构定义"></a>1.1 数据结构定义</h3><h3 id="1-2-数据的逻辑结构和物理结构"><a href="#1-2-数据的逻辑结构和物理结构" class="headerlink" title="1.2. 数据的逻辑结构和物理结构"></a>1.2. 数据的逻辑结构和物理结构</h3><ol><li>数据的逻辑结构—–从用户视图看，是面向问题的。<br>数据的物理结构—–从具体实现视图看，是面向计算机的。<br>相关的操作及其实现。</li></ol><h3 id="1-3-面向对象的概念（不重要）"><a href="#1-3-面向对象的概念（不重要）" class="headerlink" title="1.3. 面向对象的概念（不重要）"></a>1.3. 面向对象的概念（不重要）</h3><ol><li>OO:object-oriented＝object＋class＋inherit＋communicate</li></ol><h3 id="1-4-算法的概念"><a href="#1-4-算法的概念" class="headerlink" title="1.4. 算法的概念"></a>1.4. 算法的概念</h3><ol><li>Input specified，Output specified，Definiteness，Effectiveness，Fitness（五个性质）</li></ol><h3 id="1-5-所有的排序算法（算法流程、复杂度）"><a href="#1-5-所有的排序算法（算法流程、复杂度）" class="headerlink" title="1.5. 所有的排序算法（算法流程、复杂度）"></a>1.5. 所有的排序算法（算法流程、复杂度）</h3><ol><li>insertion sort</li><li>rank sort</li></ol><h3 id="1-6-递归、分治、贪心的算法思想"><a href="#1-6-递归、分治、贪心的算法思想" class="headerlink" title="1.6. 递归、分治、贪心的算法思想"></a>1.6. <strong>递归</strong>、分治、贪心的算法思想</h3><h2 id="chapter2"><a href="#chapter2" class="headerlink" title="chapter2"></a>chapter2</h2><h3 id="2-1-时间复杂度、空间复杂度的概念："><a href="#2-1-时间复杂度、空间复杂度的概念：" class="headerlink" title="2.1. 时间复杂度、空间复杂度的概念："></a>2.1. 时间复杂度、空间复杂度的概念：</h3><ol><li>the amount of memory a program needs to run to completion 运行完成程序所需要的内存空间</li><li>the amount of time a program needs to run to completion 程序运行完成所需要的时间</li><li>不考的概念：占哪些内存空间</li><li>顺序查找算法<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">SequentialSearch</span><span class="params">( <span class="type">int</span> [] a , <span class="type">int</span> x )</span> &#123;   </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> i;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(i=<span class="number">0</span>; i&lt;a.length &amp;&amp;a[i]!=x; i++)   ; </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(i= = a.length) <span class="keyword">return</span> –<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> i; </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    Total data space:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    12 bytes :  x,i,a[i],0,-1,a.length</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    each of   them cost 2 bytes</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    S(n)=0</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">*/</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>具体度量不考</li></ol><h3 id="2-2-Time-Complexity"><a href="#2-2-Time-Complexity" class="headerlink" title="2.2 Time Complexity"></a>2.2 Time Complexity</h3><ol><li><strong>大O表示法</strong>重点，尽量写Theta表示法的结果</li><li>BinarySearch的过程和复杂度<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    Example 2: Binary Search</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">        0   1  2  3  4  5  6  7   8  </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    a: -1  0  1  3  4  6  8  10  12    x = 6</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">*/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">binarySearch</span><span class="params">(Comparable [] a, Comparable x)</span>&#123;   </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">low</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">0</span>, high = a.length - <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>( low &lt;= high )&#123;   </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">mid</span> <span class="operator">=</span> ( low + high ) / <span class="number">2</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(a[mid].compareTo(x) &lt; <span class="number">0</span>) </span><br><span class="line">            low = mid + <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span>(a[mid].compareTo(x) &gt; <span class="number">0</span>) </span><br><span class="line">            high = mid – <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">return</span> mid; </span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> NOT-FOUND; </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 最好:一次       最坏:log2n     平均:O(log2n)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>辗转相除的算法流程<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="type">long</span> <span class="title function_">gcd</span><span class="params">( <span class="type">long</span> m, <span class="type">long</span> n )</span>&#123;   </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>( n != <span class="number">0</span> )&#123;    </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">long</span> <span class="variable">rem</span> <span class="operator">=</span> m % n;</span><br><span class="line">        m = n; </span><br><span class="line">        n = rem;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125; </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> m;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// O(log N)</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h2 id="Chapter3"><a href="#Chapter3" class="headerlink" title="Chapter3"></a>Chapter3</h2><h3 id="3-1-ADT"><a href="#3-1-ADT" class="headerlink" title="3.1 ADT"></a>3.1 ADT</h3><ol><li>stack：push、pop，peak</li><li>单链表：带表头和不带表头</li><li>双链表、循环链表一般不考</li></ol><h3 id="3-2-栈和队列"><a href="#3-2-栈和队列" class="headerlink" title="3.2 栈和队列"></a>3.2 栈和队列</h3><ol><li>重要，看代码</li></ol><h2 id="Chapter4"><a href="#Chapter4" class="headerlink" title="Chapter4"></a>Chapter4</h2><h3 id="4-1-概念"><a href="#4-1-概念" class="headerlink" title="4.1 概念"></a>4.1 概念</h3><ol><li>选择题小概念</li></ol><h3 id="4-2-表示方法"><a href="#4-2-表示方法" class="headerlink" title="4.2 表示方法"></a>4.2 表示方法</h3><h3 id="4-3-遍历（重点）"><a href="#4-3-遍历（重点）" class="headerlink" title="4.3 遍历（重点）"></a>4.3 遍历（重点）</h3><h3 id="4-4-String"><a href="#4-4-String" class="headerlink" title="4.4 String"></a>4.4 String</h3><h3 id="4-5-树的表示方法"><a href="#4-5-树的表示方法" class="headerlink" title="4.5 树的表示方法"></a>4.5 树的表示方法</h3><ol><li>广义表不要求</li><li>双亲表示：和并查集一起考</li><li><strong>左子女右兄弟</strong></li><li><strong>二叉树、森林、图的遍历</strong></li></ol><h3 id="4-6-线索化二叉树（常考）"><a href="#4-6-线索化二叉树（常考）" class="headerlink" title="4.6 线索化二叉树（常考）"></a>4.6 线索化二叉树（常考）</h3><h3 id="4-7-Huffman树"><a href="#4-7-Huffman树" class="headerlink" title="4.7 Huffman树"></a>4.7 Huffman树</h3><h3 id="4-8-搜索树"><a href="#4-8-搜索树" class="headerlink" title="4.8 搜索树"></a>4.8 搜索树</h3><ol><li><strong>AVL树</strong></li><li><strong>B树</strong>：不要求代码，要求画出B树及操作</li><li>算法复杂度要求掌握</li><li>算法流程</li></ol><h2 id="Chapter5"><a href="#Chapter5" class="headerlink" title="Chapter5"></a>Chapter5</h2><h3 id="5-1-散列函数"><a href="#5-1-散列函数" class="headerlink" title="5.1 散列函数"></a>5.1 散列函数</h3><ol><li>只考取余</li></ol><h3 id="5-2-解决冲突"><a href="#5-2-解决冲突" class="headerlink" title="5.2 解决冲突"></a>5.2 解决冲突</h3><ol><li>开放地址的线性探测（常考）</li><li>二次探测：解决数据堆积</li><li>双散列函数偶尔考</li><li>分离链接和链表</li></ol><h2 id="Chapter6"><a href="#Chapter6" class="headerlink" title="Chapter6"></a>Chapter6</h2><h3 id="6-1-heap"><a href="#6-1-heap" class="headerlink" title="6.1 heap"></a>6.1 heap</h3><ol><li>上滤、下滤、进堆、出堆的流程和复杂度</li><li>线性时间建堆</li><li>证明不要求</li><li>掌握堆排序：不额外占用空间</li></ol><h2 id="Chapter7"><a href="#Chapter7" class="headerlink" title="Chapter7"></a>Chapter7</h2><h3 id="7-1-最小生成树"><a href="#7-1-最小生成树" class="headerlink" title="7.1 最小生成树"></a>7.1 最小生成树</h3><h3 id="7-2-算法和优化"><a href="#7-2-算法和优化" class="headerlink" title="7.2 算法和优化"></a>7.2 算法和优化</h3><h2 id="Chapter8"><a href="#Chapter8" class="headerlink" title="Chapter8"></a>Chapter8</h2><h3 id="8-1-概念选择填空"><a href="#8-1-概念选择填空" class="headerlink" title="8.1 概念选择填空"></a>8.1 概念选择填空</h3><ol><li>生成树</li><li>极大连通子图</li></ol><h3 id="8-2-图的表达方式"><a href="#8-2-图的表达方式" class="headerlink" title="8.2 图的表达方式"></a>8.2 图的表达方式</h3><ol><li>邻接表跳过</li></ol><h3 id="8-3-最小生成树"><a href="#8-3-最小生成树" class="headerlink" title="8.3 最小生成树"></a>8.3 最小生成树</h3><h4 id="8-3-1-Prim"><a href="#8-3-1-Prim" class="headerlink" title="8.3.1 Prim"></a>8.3.1 Prim</h4><h4 id="8-3-2-Kruskal-对边进行排序，然后生成"><a href="#8-3-2-Kruskal-对边进行排序，然后生成" class="headerlink" title="8.3.2 Kruskal(对边进行排序，然后生成)"></a>8.3.2 Kruskal(对边进行排序，然后生成)</h4><h3 id="8-4-最短路径"><a href="#8-4-最短路径" class="headerlink" title="8.4 最短路径"></a>8.4 最短路径</h3><h3 id="8-5-活动网络（常考）"><a href="#8-5-活动网络（常考）" class="headerlink" title="8.5 活动网络（常考）"></a>8.5 活动网络（常考）</h3><ol><li>AOV</li><li>AOE</li></ol><h2 id="Chapter9"><a href="#Chapter9" class="headerlink" title="Chapter9"></a>Chapter9</h2><h3 id="9-1-快排（重点）"><a href="#9-1-快排（重点）" class="headerlink" title="9.1 快排（重点）"></a>9.1 快排（重点）</h3><h3 id="9-2-表格"><a href="#9-2-表格" class="headerlink" title="9.2 表格"></a>9.2 表格</h3><p><img src="/images/sort.png"></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
